Author: certainly_cerulean
Text: The first few sentences, I was worried this was gonna be about me. There's another girl in my neighborhood who I see out walking ALL the time and we only ever smile at each other but like...we know. We're both out there walking for hours on end, passing each other every time we go around the same block. It's kinda awkward bc I wanna talk to her but idk how to be like heyyy so you're anorexic too? How's it going?

Author: jocelynxxo
Text: Probably. I get really sad when I see others suffering with a probable ED and it takes everything in me to not give them a hug and tell them they're not alone cause my brain's also a pos and I'm also relapsing
